name: Nite Ize Big Dual Carabiner Plastic
description: A supersized version of the super handy S-Biner from Nite Ize®. This one’s big and burly enough to hold bikes, coiled climbing ropes, and loaded packs. You’ll find lots of uses for it around your campsite or in your home gear room.Glass-filled nylon body is light and strong.Twin stainless steel wire gates.Fits objects up to 6.4cm in diameter.Dimensions are 26 x 12 x 1.6cm.Weight-rated to 45kg (static load only).Note: this is an accessory carabiner only, and should not be used for climbing or any situation where failure could result in bodily injury or property damage.
